(9529, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>vue-router 传参：</p><p>url: http://localhost/detail/123</p><p>html: &lt;router-link :to="{name: ''detail'', params: {id: item.id} }"&gt;&lt;/router-link&gt;</p><p>routes: [<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; {<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; path: ''/detail/:id'',<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; name: ''detail'',<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; component: detail<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br>&nbsp; ]</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:56:33', '2019-10-21 22:56:33', 318, 0),
(9530, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>input readonly属性自定义值：</p><p>isReadOnly: true/false</p><p><span style="color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13.02px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);">&lt;input :readonly="isReadOnly"&gt;</span></p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:57:56', '2019-10-21 22:57:56', 318, 0),
(9531, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>vue2.0 的过滤器 filter不能在v-text内，</p><p>报错：method "orderStatusTxt" is not defined</p><p>需要这样方能生效{{ code | filterName(code) }}</p><p>-----------------------------</p><p>vue2.0可在v-html中这样使用filter:</p><p>v-html="$options.filters.fun(val)&nbsp; //在官方文档没有说明，但测试可行</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:58:19', '2019-10-21 22:58:19', 318, 0),
(9532, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">Node Sass could not find a binding for your current environment: Windows 32-bit with Node.js 6.x</span><br><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">Found bindings for the following environments:</span><br><span style="background-color:#FAEBD7;">&nbsp; - Windows 64-bit with Node.js 6.x</span></p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">- cnpm install node-sass</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:32', '2019-10-21 22:59:32', 316, 0),
(9533, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>报错：You are using the runtime-only build of Vue where the template compiler is not available</p><p><span style="color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12.6px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);">vue-template-compiler</span></p><p><a href="http://www.zhimengzhe.com/Javascriptjiaocheng/244791.html" target="_blank">http://www.zhimengzhe.com/Javascriptjiaocheng/244791.html</a></p><p><a href="http://blog.csdn.net/zhangchao19890805/article/details/53367574" target="_blank">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangchao19890805/article/details/53367574</a></p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:34', '2019-10-21 22:59:34', 316, 0),
(9534, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>报错：Failed to mount component: template or render function not defined.</p><p>好像跟模板使用了&lt;template&gt;有关</p><p>相关：<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40870433/error-failed-to-mount-component-template-or-render-function-not-defined-foun" target="_blank">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40870433/error-failed-to-mount-component-template-or-render-function-not-defined-foun</a></p><p><a href="http://www.imooc.com/article/17868" target="_blank">http://www.imooc.com/article/17868</a></p><p>const Home = require(''./components/home/index.vue''); 改成</p><p>import Home from ''./components/home/index.vue''; 就好了</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:37', '2019-10-21 22:59:37', 316, 0),
(9535, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>报错：this._init is not a function&nbsp;&nbsp;at Object.Vue$3 ...</p><p>test: /.vue$/,&nbsp; loader: ''vue'' 改成&nbsp;test: /.vue$/,&nbsp; loader: ''vue-loader'' 就好了</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:41', '2019-10-21 22:59:41', 316, 0),
