(9539, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>报错：Avoid mutating a prop directly since the value will be overwritten whenever the parent component re-renders. Instead, use a data or computed property based on the prop''s value. Prop being mutated: "transData"</p><p>// 不要直接改传参值，解决： 可通过修改对象下的属性值来传参</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:55', '2019-10-21 22:59:55', 316, 0),
(9540, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>Can''t resolve ''sass-loader'' ..&nbsp; &nbsp;-&gt; $ cnpm install sass-loader --save-dev</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Cannot find module ''node-sass''&nbsp; -&gt; $ cnpm install node-sass&nbsp;--save-dev</p>', '', '2019-10-21 22:59:58', '2019-10-21 22:59:58', 316, 0),
(9541, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>-360和QQ浏览器报错：</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">--‘对象不支持assign’：装babel-polyfill就好</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">- cnpm install&nbsp;babel-polyfill --save</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">- import ''babel-polyfill''</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">-entry: {</p><p style="margin-left: 120px;">app: [''babel-polyfill'', ''./src/index.js'']</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">}</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="background-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);">以下测试是否安装了babel-polyfill就已经支持promise而不需要再安装下面的es6-promise了？</span></span></p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">--‘XMLHttpRequest:网络错误’ &amp;&amp; ‘Unhandled promise rejection Error: Network Error’</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">- cnpm install es6-promise --save</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">import promise from ''es6-promise'';</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">promise.polyfill();</p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:00:04', '2019-10-21 23:00:04', 316, 0),
(9542, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>报错：emitting HtmlWebpackPluginFATAL ERROR: NewSpace::Rebalance Allocation failed</p><p>// 项目太大，内存不足？</p><p>全局安装increase-memory-limit<br>npm install -g increase-memory-limit<br>进入工程目录，执行：<br>increase-memory-limit</p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:00:08', '2019-10-21 23:00:08', 316, 0),
(9543, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>按需加载（懒加载）：</p><p>const A&nbsp; &nbsp; = resolve =&gt; require([''./components/a''], resolve);</p><p>export const xxx = () =&gt; import(''./index.vue''); --- // webpack 语法</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>获取当前模块dom：</p><p>this.$el</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>把当前模块放到body下一级：（有时候需要相对body做fixed定位）</p><p>document.body.appendChild(this.$el)</p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:43:17', '2019-10-21 23:43:17', 287, 0),
(9544, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>内置样式通过computed赋值：</p><p>&lt;div :style="[xxxStyle]"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</p><p>computed: {</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">xxxStyle () {</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">return true ? {''margin-left'': 0} : null</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">}</p><p>}</p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:43:24', '2019-10-21 23:43:24', 287, 0),
(9545, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>监听多个对象（A,B,C）都变化了实例swiper一次，以后的update只监听C:</p><p>------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">data - a=0, b=0, swiperWatch = 0;</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">computed - A = 列表数组A, B = 列表数组B, C = 列表数组C</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">watch :</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">A -&gt; a = 1</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">B -&gt; b = 1</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">C -&gt; if (a &amp;&amp; b) { this.swiperWatch = Math.random(); C = 列表数组}</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; else { C=Math.random()&nbsp;}</p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:43:30', '2019-10-21 23:43:30', 287, 0),
(9546, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<div>export default {</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;install: (Vue)&nbsp;=&gt; {</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for (let name of Object.keys(Components))&nbsp;{</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vue.component(Components[name][&#39;name&#39;],&nbsp;Components[name]);</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;for&nbsp;(let&nbsp;name&nbsp;of&nbsp;Object.keys(Mixins))&nbsp;{</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vue.mixin(Mixins[name]);</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;}</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for (let name in Filters)&nbsp;{</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vue.filter(name,&nbsp;Filters[name]);</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for (let name in Directives)&nbsp;{</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vue.directive(name,&nbsp;Directives[name]);</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vue.prototype.$utils =&nbsp;Utils;</div><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</div><div>};</div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>', '', '2019-10-21 23:46:31', '2019-10-21 23:46:51', 287, 0),
