(9556, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>自定义Dom:</p><p>&lt;span <span style="color:#FF0000;">slot-scope="{node, data}"</span>&gt;</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;p&gt;{{node.label}}&lt;/p&gt;</p><p>&lt;/span&gt;</p><p>slot元素:</p><p>&lt;span slot-scope="{node, data}"&gt;</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;// 作为包裹多个子元素的外容器，作判断用，最后不被渲染 ？</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;slot v-if="node.active" :node="node" :data="data"&gt;</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">&lt;svg-icon icon="#icon-test" /&gt;</p><p style="margin-left: 80px;">&lt;span&gt;{{ node.label }}&lt;/span&gt;</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;/slot&gt;</p><p>&lt;/span&gt;</p><p>vue格式：</p><p>&lt;template v-slot:default="{ node, data }"&gt; // template不被渲染，只作为判断用的外容器</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">&lt;span&gt;{{node.label}}&lt;/span&gt;</p><p>&lt;/template&gt;</p>', '', '2019-10-22 23:20:44', '2019-10-22 23:20:44', 522, 0),
(9557, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<p>过滤搜索：</p><p>对节点进行过滤时，调用 Tree 实例的filter方法，参数为关键字。此时需要设置filter-node-method，值为过滤函数<br>&lt;el-tree<br>...<br><span style="color:#FF0000;">:filter-node-method</span>="filterNode"<br>&gt;&lt;/el-tree&gt;<br>watch: {<br>&nbsp; filterText(val) {<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color:#FF0000;">&nbsp;this.$refs.tree.filter</span>(val);<br>&nbsp; }<br>},</p><p>methods: {<br>&nbsp; filterNode(value, data) {<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; if (!value) return true;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; return data.label.indexOf(value) !== -1;<br>&nbsp; }<br>},</p>', '', '2019-10-22 23:20:56', '2019-10-22 23:20:56', 522, 0),
(9558, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<div>&lt;el-tree</div><div>:auto-expand-parent="true"&nbsp; // 测试无效？</div><div>:highlight-current="true"&nbsp; // 测试无效？</div><div>&gt;&lt;/el-tree&gt;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>// <span style="color:#FF0000;">高亮当前路由对应node</span>(如果是下级，其父级展开)</div><div>highlightCurrentKey () {</div><div>let routeName = this.$route.name;</div><div>this.$nextTick(() =&gt; {</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="white-space:pre;">&nbsp;</span>this.$refs.tree.<span style="color:#FF0000;">setCurrentKey</span>(routeName);</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="white-space:pre;">&nbsp;</span>let flag = this.menu.some(x =&gt; x.name === routeName);</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="white-space:pre;">&nbsp;</span>if (!flag) { this.defaultExpandedKeys = [routeName]; }</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; });</div><div>},</div>', '', '2019-10-22 23:21:03', '2019-10-22 23:21:03', 522, 0),
